---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How A Green Family collects, uses, and protects information on agreenfamily.com."
>
  <article class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-14">

    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl text-forest mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-ink-muted text-sm mb-10">Last updated: May 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-green prose-lg max-w-none">

      <p>
        This page explains what information agreenfamily.com collects, how it's used, and what choices you have.
        We've tried to write this in plain language rather than legal boilerplate. If you have questions,
        email us at <a href="mailto:hello@agreenfamily.com">hello@agreenfamily.com</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Information we collect</h2>
      <p>
        We collect very little. Specifically:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Newsletter signups.</strong> If you subscribe to our newsletter, we collect your email address.
          We use this only to send you the newsletter. We do not sell or share your email with third parties.
          You can unsubscribe at any time using the link in any email we send.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Contact emails.</strong> If you email us at hello@agreenfamily.com, we receive and store
          that email in order to respond to you.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Analytics.</strong> We use Cloudflare Web Analytics to understand how many people visit the site
          and which pages are popular. Cloudflare Analytics does not use cookies and does not track individual users
          across sites. No personal data is collected by this tool.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        This site itself does not set cookies. However, third-party services we link to — including Amazon —
        may set cookies on your device when you click through to their sites.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Amazon:</strong> As a participant in the Amazon Associates Program, links to Amazon on this site
        include an affiliate tracking tag. When you click an Amazon link, Amazon may set a cookie on your device
        to track any resulting purchases. This cookie is governed by Amazon's privacy policy, available at
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">amazon.com/privacy</a>.
        You can opt out of Amazon's interest-based advertising at
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/adprefs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">amazon.com/adprefs</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Walmart and Target:</strong> Links to Walmart and Target on this site may include affiliate
        tracking parameters managed through the Impact affiliate network. Their privacy policies apply when
        you visit their sites.
      </p>

      <h2>Affiliate links</h2>
      <p>
        Some articles on this site contain affiliate links to Amazon, Walmart, and Target. If you purchase
        through one of these links, we earn a small commission at no extra cost to you.
        See our full <a href="/disclosure">affiliate disclosure</a> for details.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-party services</h2>
      <p>
        We use the following third-party services to operate this site:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Cloudflare Pages</strong> — hosts this website. Cloudflare's privacy policy applies to infrastructure-level data.</li>
        <li><strong>Beehiiv</strong> — manages our newsletter. If you subscribe, your email is stored on Beehiiv's platform, subject to their privacy policy.</li>
        <li><strong>Web3Forms</strong> — processes newsletter signup form submissions.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We do not use Google Analytics, Facebook Pixel, or any advertising tracking tools.
      </p>

      <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
      <p>
        This site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information
        from children. If you believe a child has submitted information through this site, contact us
        at <a href="mailto:hello@agreenfamily.com">hello@agreenfamily.com</a> and we will delete it.
      </p>

      <h2>Your rights</h2>
      <p>
        If you have subscribed to our newsletter and want your email removed from our records, unsubscribe
        using the link in any email or contact us directly. We will remove your data promptly.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you are located in the European Union, you have additional rights under the GDPR, including the
        right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. Contact us at
        <a href="mailto:hello@agreenfamily.com">hello@agreenfamily.com</a> to exercise these rights.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>
        If we make significant changes to this policy, we will update the date at the top of this page.
        We encourage you to review it periodically.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this privacy policy or how we handle data:
        <a href="mailto:hello@agreenfamily.com">hello@agreenfamily.com</a>
      </p>

    </div>

  </article>
</Layout>
